OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,FThe extent of the disturbance is not
OL,7,Fyet known but has confirmed its
OL,8,Fofficers are looking into the cause of
OL,9,Fthe issue and both Bishopston Sports
OL,10,FCentre and Bishopston Comprehensive
OL,11,FSchool.
OL,13,FThe confirmation came after staff at
OL,14,FBishopston Sports Centre, which is run
OL,15,Fby Freedom Leisure and housed in the
OL,16,Fmain school building, is open to
OL,17,Fmembers from outside the school
OL,18,Fcommunity, announced on social media
OL,19,Fthe centre would be temporarily closed.
