OL,6,FBishopston Sports Centre has since
OL,7,Freopened.
OL,9,FAn initial post on social media last
OL,10,FFriday (9 February) said: "Due to
OL,11,Fcircumstances outside of our control,
OL,12,Fthe centre will not be open today and
OL,13,Ffor the rest of the weekend.
OL,15,F"We apologise for any inconvenience
OL,16,Fcaused and thank you for your
OL,17,Funderstanding. All of our other
OL,18,Fcentres across Swansea are open as
OL,19,Fusual."
