OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,Fsaid in a statement: "As a precaution
OL,7,Fsome of the utility supplies have been
OL,8,Fdisconnected which means pupils cannot
OL,9,Freturn after the half-term break.
OL,11,F"Work is continuing to identify the
OL,12,Fcause and any remedial work required.
OL,14,F"The council and specialist
OL,15,Fcontractors are working to find
OL,16,Falternate solutions to restoring
OL,17,Fsupplies to the school.School staff
OL,18,Fare working on options for providing
OL,19,Feducation to pupils whilst the school
OL,20,Fbuildings are closed.
