OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,FBishopston Primary School is
OL,7,Funaffected and will reopen as normal
OL,8,Fafter the half-term break.
OL,10,FThe nearby leisure centre, within a
OL,11,Fseparate building on a different part
OL,12,Fof the site, has its own supplies and
OL,13,Fwill be able to reopen next week."
OL,15,FRobert Smith, Cabinet Member for
OL,16,FEducation, said: "This situation is
OL,17,Fbeyond our control but everything
OL,18,Fpossible is being done to get pupils
OL,19,Fback into class as soon as we can.
