OL,3,CSwansea school to stay closed after
OL,4,Chalf-term due to 'ground movement'
OL,6,F"We fully appreciate the temporary
OL,7,Fclosure of the school buildings will
OL,8,Fcause disruption for pupils and their
OL,9,Ffamilies but the safety of pupils and
OL,10,Fstaff is our number one priority.
OL,12,F"Our teams and contractors are pulling
OL,13,Fout all the stops to get the buildings
OL,14,Freopened as soon as we possibly can
OL,15,Fand we will update pupils and their
OL,16,Ffamilies as soon as we can.
OL,18,F"We will know more once the ground
OL,19,Finvestigations have been completed.
