OL,6,F"In the meantime we are working on
OL,7,Foptions for providing education to
OL,8,Fpupils whilst the school buildings
OL,9,Fremain closed and these will be
OL,10,Fdirectly communicated with families.
OL,12,F"Arrangements are also being made for
OL,13,Fpupils entitled to free school meals."
